<!DOCTYPE html>
 <html  lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="utf-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width,initial-scale=1.0,user-scalable=no">
    <title>图片生成器</title>
    <meta name="description" content="">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/stylesheets/reset.css">
    <style>
      @font-face {
        font-family: "SourceHanSerifCN";
        src: url(/font/SourceHanSerifCN-Bold.otf);
      }
      body {
        background-color: #032692;
        width: 100vw;
        height: 100vh;
        overflow: hidden;
      }
      .poster {
        width: 100%;
        height: 100%;
        padding-top: 32px;
        box-sizing: border-box;
        position: relative;
      }
      .headImg {
        width: 310px;
        
        margin: 0 auto;
        position: relative;
        z-index: 2;
      }
      .imgBox {
        width: 100%;
        height: 290px;
        overflow: hidden;
        position: relative;
        z-index: 2;
        border: 3px solid #fff;
        border-radius: 10px;
        box-sizing: border-box;
      }
      .headImg .img {
        width: 100%;
        display: block;
        box-sizing: border-box;
      }
      .headImg::after {
        content: '';
        width: 100%;
        height: 100%;
        position: relative;
        background-color: #E41625;
        border: 3px solid #fff;
        border-radius: 10px;
        box-sizing: border-box;
        z-index: 1;
        margin: 7px;
        position: absolute;
        top: 3px;
        left: 2px;
      }
      .title {
        font-size:40px;
        font-family:SourceHanSerifCN;
        font-weight:bold;
        color:#fff;
        line-height:1;
        text-align: center;
        margin: 30px 0 17px;
        letter-spacing: 5px;
      }
      .p {
        font-size:16px;
        font-family:SourceHanSerifCN;
        font-weight:300;
        color:#fff;
        line-height:24px;
        padding-left: 34px;
      }
      .box {
        padding: 0 4px;
        display: inline-block;
        position: relative;
        margin: 0 2px;
        font-family:SourceHanSerifCN;
        font-weight:300;
      }
      .box::after {
        content: '';
        width: 100%;
        height: 6px;
        background-color: #E41625;
        position: absolute;
        left: 0;
        bottom: 3px;
        z-index: -1;
      }
      .tis {
        line-height: 1;
        font-size: 0;
      }
      .tis span {
        font-size:18px;
        font-family:SourceHanSerifCN;
        font-weight:bold;
        color:#fff;
        line-height:1;
        margin-top: 12px;
        margin-left: 34px;
        letter-spacing: 2px;
        display: inline-block;
        position: relative;
      }
      .tis span::after {
        content: '';
        width: 100%;
        height: 6px;
        background-color: #E41625;
        position: absolute;
        left: 0;
        bottom: 0;
        z-index: -1;
      }
      .footer {
        position: absolute;
        width: 100%;
        height: 63px;
        background-color: #fff;
        left: 0;
        bottom: 0;
      }
      .footer .p {
        width:130px;
        font-size:12px;
        font-family:SourceHanSerifCN;
        color:#000;
        line-height:18px;
        top: 14px;
        left: 32px;
        position: absolute;
        padding: 0;
      }
      .footerImg {
        width: 60px;
        position: absolute;
        top: -18px;
        right: 23px;
      }
      .erweima {
        width: 100%;
        display: block;
      }
      .tips {
        width: 100%;
        height: 14px;
        background-color: #032692;
        text-align: center;
      }
      .tips span {
        display: block;
        height: 14px;
        font-size:12px;
        font-family:SourceHanSerifCN;
        color:#fff;
        transform: scale(0.8);
        line-height:12px;
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="poster">
      <div class="headImg">
        <div class="imgBox"><img class="img" src=<%= img %> ></div>
      </div>
      <p class="title">追逐梦想的青年</p>
      <p class="p">我是<span class="box"><%= name %></span> 我是<span class="box"><%= introduce %></span></p>
      <p class="p">我可以<span class="desc"><%= desc1 %></span></p>
      <p class="p">也可以<span class="desc"><%= desc2 %></span></p>
      <p class="p">还可以<span class="desc"><%= desc3 %></span></p>
      <p class="p">2020我想<span class="desc"><%= desc4 %></span></p>
      <p class="tis"><span># 野兽青年 和你一起勇敢向前 #</span></p>
      <div class="footer">
        <p class="p">小程序搜索：野兽青年和你一起开启热爱</p>
        <div class="footerImg">
          <img class="erweima" src="/images/youngBeast.png" />
          <p class="tips"><span>扫码制作</span></p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </body>
  <script>
    (function(){
        var calc = function(){
            var docElement = document.documentElement;
            var clientWidthValue = docElement.clientWidth > 750 ? 750 : docElement.clientWidth;
            docElement.style.fontSize = 100*(clientWidthValue/750) + 'px';
        }
        calc();
        window.addEventListener('resize', calc);
    })();
    </script>
</html>